properties.property:
WHA- How do you not know abo- AH! You must be from the surface net!
The Ranking is the way of the undernet, the power of the strong.
... at least...
That's what it's SUPPOSED to be...
But basically, the Ranking sees that there are always 10 ranked navis at any time. You as an unranked navi can only challenge the rank 10 navi. They can either give it to you for doing a task, or you must defeat them in combat. Either way, once you beat the navi, you take their place in the ranking, and they take yours. Be careful though, this will lead to rivalry amongst the ranked navis.
